This directory holds the scripts used in the ubuntu-debian packages.


PRODUCTION PACKAGE
production directory - holds the production version package scripts
Directory structure of package.
--Note the maintenance scripts need broad execution privileges
--Note when gzip something use --best switch
/var/www/libreehr (this contains source, obviously not included here)
/usr/share/applications/libreehr.desktop
/usr/share/doc/libreehr/README.Debian
/usr/share/doc/libreehr/changelog.Debian.gz
/usr/share/doc/libreehr/copyright
/usr/share/man/man8/libreehr.8.gz
/DEBIAN/control
/DEBIAN/preinst
/DEBIAN/postinst
/DEBIAN/prerm
/DEBIAN/postrm
/DEBIAN/config
/DEBIAN/templates
/etc/apache2/sites-available/libreehr.conf


DEVELOPMENT CVS PACKAGE
development directory - hold the development version package scripts
Directory structure of package:
--Note the maintenance scripts need broad execution privileges
--Note when gzip something use --best switch
/usr/share/applications/git-libreehr.desktop
/usr/share/doc/git-libreehr/README.Debian
/usr/share/doc/git-libreehr/changelog.Debian.gz
/usr/share/doc/git-libreehr/copyright
/usr/share/man/man8/git-libreehr.8.gz
/DEBIAN/control
/DEBIAN/preinst
/DEBIAN/postinst
/DEBIAN/prerm
/DEBIAN/postrm
/DEBIAN/config
/DEBIAN/templates
/etc/apache2/sites-available/git-libreehr.conf
